# ============================================================
# mulu-marketing/ is an INDEPENDENT React/Vite project that
# lives next to the JSP coursework for convenience but is
# NEVER bundled by Maven and NEVER deployed by the AWS / Docker
# scripts in scripts/. It has its own node_modules, package.json,
# and Vite build (mulu-marketing/dist/). Keep it ignored here so
# nothing accidentally crosses the boundary.
# ============================================================
mulu-marketing/node_modules/
mulu-marketing/dist/
mulu-marketing/.vite/